<item>
            <title>[SPARK-11063] Spark TaskSetManager doesn&apos;t use Receiver&apos;s scheduling executors</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-11063</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The format of RDD&apos;s preferredLocations must be hostname but the format of Streaming Receiver&apos;s scheduling executors is hostport. So it doesn&apos;t work.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
